name: jewel_of_the_rose_croix
description:
The Louisiana state flag depicts a pelican feeding its young with blood from a wound in her chest. The imagery has ancient christian and masonic roots, originally adapted from the legend of the phoenix siting on a nest of flames. 
A rendition of the Louisiana state flag made from collaged GAN generated elements. 

This was minted in order to aid the recovery after Hurricane Ida in August 2021. The proceeds from all of the primary sales of this NFT will be donated to imaginewaterworks.org, an organization focused on climate justice, water management, and disaster readiness and response.
